            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "strange to put `_` for a parameter. why not just omit it?\r\n\r\nwhen a parameter is unused, but the one after it is used, then it makes sense to name the unused one something like `_foo`. but i'm not aware of any reason to name a parameter `_` if it is not followed by *used* parameters.\r\n\r\nsame for all other cases in this PR",
